# Skill Transparency

- When using a project or personal skill, explicitly name it in a user-facing update before or while applying it.
- Prefer short phrasing such as: `Using the local commit-message skill for humanaity-mcp, I reviewed the repo changes and suggest:`
- If no skill is being used, do not claim one is active.
- Keep the note concise and only mention skills that materially affect the work.
